ome with an attachment that allows you to cut your vegetables into spaghetti-like strips. Otherwise, peel and very thinly slice your vegetables into narrow strips by hand.","You can marinate your own tofu using the marinade in the Honey ginger tofu with greens recipe, which can be found on this recipe chip. You can also purchase marinated tofu at major supermarkets.","For extra flavour, season your soup with Wakame gomasio. You can find the Wakame gomasio recipe on this recipe chip.","Red miso paste is also sold as red soya bean paste.","This soup is a source of calcium, zinc, iron and protein."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","4 portions"]}